title: Episode 13: Plywood Paraphernalia
description:
Today's Proceedings:  A person jealous of his friend's wife, a person washing their behind in unfamiliar territory, and a dad experiencing Grand Theft Auto first hand.  We also talk about a local store with plywood paraphernalia and read some hand written haikus by non-other than Christian!
